  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 stale input data)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package contains a subtle epistemic weakener: the primary viscosity and rheology dataset (dataVintage 2025-10-01) predates the model revision date (2026-02-15), meaning the dataset reflects a prior model build. Re-validation against the updated model is described as planned but not yet completed.",
