      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or GCI analysis on at least three systematically refined meshes; GCI < 5% on hemolysis QoI.",
      "rationale": "Three-mesh GCI study completed; GCI on NIH QoI is 7.4%, exceeding the 5% threshold at required level 4. Mesh refinement in the impeller tip-gap region was limited by computational budget."
    },
    {
