    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the package on the basis that the seven assessed factors collectively demonstrate partial but sufficient evidence for the intended submission stage. Six factors remain as epistemic gaps flagged for resolution prior to final regulatory submission. The blood rheology dataset (vintage 2025-10-01) predating the model revision (2026-02-15) is noted; re-validation is planned for Q2 2026 and is considered acceptable given the low sensitivity of bulk viscosity to impeller geometry changes at the current assessment stage.",
